enb_long_title: Thirteenth Session of the Subsidiary Bodies of the UNFCCC
section_title: IMPACT OF SINGLE PROJECTS ON EMISSIONS IN THE COMMITMENT PERIOD
sentences: Chair Dovland noted that no submissions had been made by Parties on the matter by 17 July 2000, as requested by SBSTA-11.

Following statements by ICELAND and other Annex I countries, he concluded that full agreement had yet to be reached, and requested Ole Plougmann (Denmark) to conduct informal consultations on the issue.
